						<p>There’s plenty that can be done to improve your connection and your game.</p>
						<p>The first step is to get the best connection to your console or PC.</p>
						<h2 class="mt-4">Get off Wi-Fi and reach for the ethernet cable</h2>
						<p>You’ve heard this one before.</p>
						<p>Wired connections offer better throughput, lower latency, and more stable connections than wireless.</p>
